name: Before One Week Of The Maturity
query:
select 
    bank_account,
    amount_invested,
    date_of_deposit,
    date_of_maturity,
    net_interest,
    rate_of_interest,
    no_of_days,
    tds,
    interest_amount,
    before_one_week_of_the_maturity
    from 
`tabFixed Deposit Control Register`
report_name: Before One Week Of The Maturity
